<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card-about">
    <h1>Devan Roy Walker</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
              <div class="skill">
                <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                <div class="progress">
                  <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  >
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7">
        <p>
          Devan is an avid adventurist, who appreciates the beauty of what the world brings, but strives to utilize what it
          gives. Looking to this canvas he tries to bring this feel to his projects, hobbies and daily routine.
        </p>
        <p>
          His belief of beauty, simplicity and functionality is always a goal that he tries to improve on every day.
          Productivity works in the same fashion, with a balance of happiness, curiosity and drive, the opportunity to
          achieve something beyond the ordinary will present itself.
        </p>
        <p>
          <button
              class="btn btn-primary"
              type="button"
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#jobHistory"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              District Manager
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Problem Solver
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Bottega
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Jordan Applied Technology Center
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

